:::Torca/Ratchet/Sideswipe/Sky Lynx:::

::Torca dodges the grenade, but gets hit by 1 blast and both the stinger 
missles.  He fires 9 explosive shells at Sixshot, 8 at Ares, and 8 at 
Bumblebee::
~~~~~
::Ratchet was hit by 2 of the blasts and 1 of the stinger missles. he fired 1 
tusk missle at Sixshot, 1 at Injector, and 15 shots from each gun at 
Manterror::
~~~~~
::Sideswipe destroyed the missles and fired 2 missles and 25 shots at Double 
Punch::
~~~~~
::Sky Lynx destroyed the missles but was hit by both stinger missles and 2 of 
the bolts. He fired 2 missles from one gun at Double Punch and fired 2 
missles from his other gun, 1 at Bumblebee, and 1 at Reflector::

--part1_78.ecefb34.2787fb89_boundary
